hero_subhead: "You have pretty much everything you need to build it right here"
hero_cta: "Learn my workflow"
featured_headline: "I'm featured on"
membership_headline: "A place for intermediate-level web designers to fine tune their ZF skills"
testimonial_headline: "What people are saying about James"
